  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "- Use traveling light to get onto Shelf (2)\n- Use lens 1 to burn rope
    holding trash can lid, letting the player cross to the shelf \n- Use lens 1 to
    burn Burnable Planks 1 so they're not blocking the ingredient\n- walk to Shelf
    (1) and drop onto the flour bag, pushing the ingredient into the pot (might have
    to drop something on it if Ryan doesn't want physical interaction)\n- Drop down
    to Counter (3) and use Lens 2 to burn Burnable Plank 2, making Ingredient 2 slide
    down into the pot\n- Chef tells you to light the stove. Use lens 2 to do so to
    cook the stew\n- chef happy, transition to level select\n- Optionally can light
    the Unlit Lantern to use it for Traveling Light (so no softlock)"
